snippet.title: Sherlock Chapter One - Developer Presentation - Future Games Show
snippet.description: We've got a new look at Sherlock Chapter One! Here’s the producer and community manager from Frogwares to tell us more about the game’s setting and how they plan to create a truly open world detective game.
